txt.en: 'Hurry up and open it!'
Sunken Labyrinth
'Can't you do anything quickly?'
'Those slugs look tasty.'
'I give up. We're lost.'
'We are Sauron's secret. We are the Under-host!'
'The Under-host shall be victorious!'
'I'll blow you to bits, you cowards!'
The Rangers warned of foul creatures lurking within these tunnels.
'Time to die!'
The sounds of organized Orcs echo ahead.
'I'll finish you off, right now!'
A hunched figure ahead runs away as they spot you.
'Everything all right up here?'
The mysterious figure vanished in the shadows.
The mysterious figure watches you from the doorway, then flees.
While the mysterious figure's identity remains hidden, it is certain he has fled above ground.
Before you stands the stronghold of the Under-host.
'This should hold them.'
'Barad Nemorn was a fool's camp. Now I am in charge down here!'
'The Under-host will crush you all!'
The sounds of chains cease.
'Hey, what's that noise!'
'I'm not the one who got us lost on patrol.'
'No one gets in here!'
'Stand your ground!'
Something large stalks the ruined halls that lay ahead of you.
'Fresh bodies from the chopping block. Quickly, collect them!'
The sounds of chains notch their way through some sort of hidden mechanism.
'Our leader will be pleased by this bounty of corpses!'
'I'm working as fast as I can!'
'Welcome to my home. I'll eat your body and leave the bones!'
'I will not fail the Dark Lord.'
'Time to fall into darkness!'
'I'll bring down the city!'
'What gives you the right to enter the keep of the Under-host?'
'I am Muzgásh, leader of this great secret army of Sauron!'
'I forged this command after a misfortunate invasion at Barad Nemorn.'
'Those fools who ousted me from my post there will one day pay.'
'But now I have gained new power and await Sauron's call.'
'We will rise from the darkness and take Gondor by surprise!'
'I see your fear through the flames!'
'You worthless scum are all that stands in my way.'
'Let it burn!'
'For that, you will surely burn...'
'Let the fires engulf you!'
'I'll burn you all down!'
'Stop complaining and keep searching for the ones who wandered off!'
'Remind me to catch one of those yummy slugs after we find the others.'
'You'll never get by us!'
'Come swift my little Orcs!'
'I await Sauron's command!'
'Kill these pests!'
'Defend this hall!'
'If you see the intruders, kill them.'
'Orcs, we're under attack!'
'I can hear them coming our way.'
'Orcs, hear my call!'
'Muzgásh will see to your death if we do not!'
'The Under-host will prevail!'
'You'll make a good snack!'
'Incinerate!'
